      • selectTarget

        public java.lang.Integer selectTarget(double x)
        Returns a particular process based on an input between 0 and the total weight, with processes sorted numerically by ID number.

        So if w_i is the weight of process i, then you'll get back

        0 <= x < w_1 --> return process 1's id w_1 <= x < w_1 + w_2 --> return process 2's id ... w_n-1 <= x < sum(w) --> return process n's id
